item.title: Innwa Bank

item.title: Myanmar Internal Revenue Department
item.description: From Distributed Denial of Secrets RELEASE Myanmar Internal Revenue Department Tax filings from Myanmar’s Internal Revenue Department (IRD). The data includes all tax filings and supporting documents from 2021. DATASET DETAILS COUNTRIES Myanmar TYPE Hack SOURCE Sugondese Electronic Army FILE SIZE 446 GB How to Request Access MORE REFERENCES ICIJ investigation EDITOR NOTES ReadMe.txt from the source Tax filings from the Myanmar’s Internal Revenue Department (IRD), a state agency that has been illegally controlled by the Myanmar military since the coup on February 1, 2021.
